# fw-core-client

Flywheel Core HTTP API client.

## Installation

Add as a [`poetry`](https://python-poetry.org/docs/) dependency to your project:

```bash
poetry add fw-core-client
```

## Usage

```python
from fw_core_client import get_client

core_client = get_client(
    client_name="my-app",
    client_version="1.0",
    api_key="site.flywheel.io:699uxdIh2wmqtdDyLJ",
)
projects = core_client.get("/projects")
project_labels = [proj.label for proj in projects]
```

## Development

Install the project with dependencies using `poetry` and enable [`pre-commit`](https://pre-commit.com/):

```bash
poetry install
pre-commit install
```

